    "title": "Fear the Swarm!",
    "description": "Always corrosive. Shots detonate on impact, dealing splash damage equal to 80% of the weapon's damage; the splash is treated as grenade damage for bonuses. DAHL: aiming down sights switches to a 6-round burst. Reduced accuracy, higher elemental effect chance, and the burst rounds carry the corrosive splash effect."
